{"name":"Sigurd Steamsinger","size":"medium","type":"Humanoid","tag":"any race","alignment":"any alignment","hitDice":"13","armorName":"other","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":1,"otherArmorDesc":"16 (Propellant Breastplate)","speed":"25","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"17","dexPoints":"10","conPoints":"16","intPoints":"18","wisPoints":"14","chaPoints":"9","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"9","customCr":"6 (2,300 XP)","customProf":3,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The mage can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The mage regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the mage can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the mage can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The mage can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the mage's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the mage's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the mage dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Dwarven Resilience","desc":"[MON] has advantage on saving throws against poison, spells, and illusions, as well as to resist being charmed or paralyzed."},{"name":"Artificer","desc":"[MON] is proficient with all tools and has double proficiency with smith's tools and alchemists tools."},{"name":"Spellcasting","desc":"[MON] is a 13th-level half-caster. His spellcasting ability is Intelligence (spell save DC [INT SAVE], [INT ATK] to hit with spell attacks). [MON] has the following spells prepared:\n\n\n> * Cantrips (at will): _create bonfire, mage hand, prestidigitation_\n> * 1st level (4 slots): _detect magic, identify, grease, shield_\n> * 2nd level (3 slots): _enlarge/reduce, heat metal_\n> * 3rd level (3 slots): _elemental weapon, glyph of warding, dispel magic_\n> * 4th level (1 slots): _reslilient sphere_"},{"name":"Propellent Breastplate","desc":"Whenever a creature hits [MON] with a melee attack, it needs to make a DC [INT SAVE] strength saving throw or be pushed back 15ft."}],"actions":[{"name":"Multiattack","desc":"[MON] makes two attacks with _Steelbreaker_"},{"name":"Steelbreaker","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [STR ATK +1] to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [STR 1D8+1] bludgeoning damage, [1d8] force damage."},{"name":"Fume hood (1/day)","desc":"[MON] shoves a creature's head in a stinky sack. [MON] attempts to grapple a creature within 5ft, if successful, the creature is blinded. While blinded, at the start of it's turn it must make a DC [INT SAVE] constitution save or it must spend all of it's movement and actions wretching. A creature can remove the satchel as an action if it's not wretching."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Follow-Up","desc":"If [MON] hit the same creature with two _Steelbreaker_ attacks this turn, the creature and any other creatures in a 15ft line must make a DC [INT SAVE] strength save or take [1d6] bludgeoning damage and be knocked prone."},{"name":"Fire-Eater (1/day)","desc":"[MON] activates an amulet and gains immunity to fire damage for one minute. He can end the effect early as an action to breathe fire in a 20ft cone. Creatures in the code must make a DC [INT SAVE] dexterity saving through or take [2d6] damage for each round the effect was active."}],"reactions":[{"name":"Shield","desc":"[MON] casts _shield_."}],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"int","order":3},{"name":"wis","order":4}],"skills":[{"name":"arcana","stat":"int","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"history","stat":"int"},{"name":"intimidation","stat":"cha"},{"name":"investigation","stat":"int"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[{"name":"Aire","speaks":true},{"name":"Common","speaks":true},{"name":"Dwarvish","speaks":true}],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"Sigurd","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":3,"damage":[]}